1 0 0 1 56.0 599.0 Tm (The close in four steps) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 582.0 Tm (1. Summarise the relevant thing they said in one sentence.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 568.0 Tm (2. Ask an interest question: "Is that worth 20 minutes to look at properly?") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 554.0 Tm (3. Only if yes, offer two specific times.) Tj
